BUSINESS LOGIC FOR VIRTUAL UNIVERSITY

1)The virtual university should consist of diffrent courses in which students would enrol.  
The required fees for diffrent courses needs to be paid by the students online.

2)After successful payment of fees, students should be given access to the lectures and study materials.

3)A URL should be given to the students to access the related course study materials 
and lectures and also the study materials should be dispatched to the students to their address through any postal service.

4)The faculty would be able to update the study materials in the online repository.

5)The examination should be scheduled and the examination should be conducted. After the evaluation the results should be declared.

6)E-certificate should be mailed to the students and the certificate should be dispatched to the students address.
